<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 16:08:45 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>朴总理警告社交媒体“武器化”以勒索公务员</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-pm-warns-of-weaponisation-of-social-media-to-blackmail-and-pressurise-civil-servants/articleshow/107829450.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107829450.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 15:19:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-pm-warns-of-weaponisation-of-social-media-to-blackmail-and-pressurise-civil-servants/articleshow/107829450.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者阻止前往加沙的援助车队</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-protesters-block-aid-convoys-bound-for-gaza-latest-news/articleshow/107828207.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107828207.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列抗议者聚集在以色列和埃及之间的尼扎纳边境哨所，阻止急需的援助进入饱受战争蹂躏的加沙地带。抗议者之一大卫·鲁德曼 (David Rudman) 为自己的行为辩解说：“鉴于我们所处的情况，这是可以接受的。”然而，此时正值饥荒威胁笼罩加沙，加剧了持续战争造成的本已严峻的状况。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 14:09:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-protesters-block-aid-convoys-bound-for-gaza-latest-news/articleshow/107828207.cms</guid></item><item><title>由于加沙战争影响了国内生产总值，以色列经济萎缩</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-economy-shrinks-by-one-fifth-in-final-quarter-due-to-gaza-war/articleshow/107827965.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107827965.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最后一个季度下降 19.4% 的原因是持续不断的加沙战争对这个高科技国家经济的影响。总体而言，2023年以色列GDP增长2.0%，低于以色列央行10月战争爆发后预测的2.3%。自战争爆发以来，该国出现了大规模的劳动力短缺和旅游业的崩溃。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 14:00:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-economy-shrinks-by-one-fifth-in-final-quarter-due-to-gaza-war/articleshow/107827965.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃菲尔铁塔罢工导致世界上最受欢迎的纪念碑之一对游客关闭</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/strike-at-the-eiffel-tower-closes-one-of-the-worlds-most-popular-monuments-to-visitors/articleshow/107828075.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107828075.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;由于财务管理不善而举行罢工，埃菲尔铁塔周一拒绝了游客。入口处有一个牌子为关闭而道歉。在夏季奥运会之前，这座巴黎热门地标的游客人数一直在激增。计划周一参观埃菲尔铁塔的游客在其网站上收到了多语言服务中断的警告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/strike-at-the-eiffel-tower-closes-one-of-the-worlds-most-popular-monuments-to-visitors/articleshow/107828075.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾称中国海警在前线岛屿附近登上台湾船只</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coast-guard-boarded-taiwanese-boat-near-frontline-islands-taiwan-says/articleshow/107827305.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107827305.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，中国海警人员在中国沿海附近的台湾控制岛屿附近短暂登上了一艘台湾旅游船。该事件发生之前，中国宣布加强金门群岛周围的执法活动，两名中国公民逃离台湾海岸警卫队，在距离金门太近的地方死亡。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-coast-guard-boarded-taiwanese-boat-near-frontline-islands-taiwan-says/articleshow/107827305.cms</guid></item><item><title>如果欧盟不达成协议，西班牙将对暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-to-impose-sanctions-on-violent-israeli-settlers-if-eu-deal-fails/articleshow/107827240.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107827240.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;西班牙外交部长何塞·曼努埃尔·阿尔瓦雷斯宣布，如果欧盟未能就此事达成协议，西班牙准备对约旦河西岸暴力的以色列定居者实施制裁。在布鲁塞尔举行的欧盟外长会议期间，西班牙将推动这些制裁的批准。阿尔巴雷斯表示，“如果达不成协议，西班牙将单独对暴力定居者实施制裁。”</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 13:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/spain-to-impose-sanctions-on-violent-israeli-settlers-if-eu-deal-fails/articleshow/107827240.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称俄罗斯以“猛烈火力”攻击南部地区</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-russia-attacking-with-heavy-fire-in-southern-region/articleshow/107825838.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107825838.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰陆军发言人周一表示，莫斯科上周取得九个月来最重大的领土进展后，乌克兰军队在扎波罗热南部地区面临俄罗斯军队的“猛烈火力”。乌克兰军方发言人德米特罗·利霍维周一表示，俄罗斯目前正在罗博泰尼村附近发动多次袭击，这是乌克兰在去年的反攻中成功收复失地的少数几个地方之一。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:18:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-says-russia-attacking-with-heavy-fire-in-southern-region/articleshow/107825838.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称乌克兰毒害了两个被吞并的乌克兰省份的州长</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-ukraine-poisoned-governors-of-two-annexed-ukrainian-provinces/articleshow/107825888.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107825888.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯国防部周一表示，乌克兰毒害了莫斯科任命的乌克兰赫尔松和卢甘斯克地区州长，尽管两人都还活着。该部在网上发布的简报中表示，乌克兰于 2023 年 12 月毒害了莫斯科任命的卢甘斯克州长列昂尼德·帕塞奇尼克 (Leonid Pasechnik)，并于 2022 年 8 月毒害了赫尔松州州长弗拉基米尔·萨尔多 (Vladimir Saldo)。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 12:22:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russia-says-ukraine-poisoned-governors-of-two-annexed-ukrainian-provinces/articleshow/107825888.cms</guid></item><item><title>加沙卫生部表示，以色列与哈马斯的战争造成超过 29,092 名巴勒斯坦人死亡、69,028 人受伤</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-health-ministry-says-over-29092-palestinians-killed-69028-injured-in-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/107821418.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107821418.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部周日表示，自10月7日以色列-哈马斯战争爆发以来，已有超过29,092名巴勒斯坦人丧生，69,028人受伤。加沙冲突始于10月7日，当时哈马斯枪手突破边界据以色列报道，以色列国防军袭击了以色列城镇，造成约 1,200 人死亡，并将 250 名人质拖回加沙。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:16:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/gaza-health-ministry-says-over-29092-palestinians-killed-69028-injured-in-israel-hamas-war/articleshow/107821418.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟启动保护红海航运的任务</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-launches-mission-to-protect-red-sea-shipping/articleshow/107824616.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107824616.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟已启动一项任务，保护红海国际航运免受也门胡塞叛军的袭击。该任务旨在确保海上贸易路线的安全，并防止胡塞武装的袭击造成任何干扰。欧盟主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩宣布了这一倡议，强调需要保护该地区的航运。此次任务是欧盟维护红海地区稳定与安全承诺的一部分。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:39:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-launches-mission-to-protect-red-sea-shipping/articleshow/107824616.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰称俄罗斯三天内损失六架战机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-loses-six-warplanes-in-three-days-ukraine-says/articleshow/107824655.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107824655.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;陆军参谋长奥列克桑德尔·西尔斯基(Oleksandr Syrskyi)表示，乌克兰军方周一击落了另外两架俄罗斯战机，这些战机用于向基辅军队投掷高破坏性的制导炸弹。西尔斯基在 Telegram 上表示，被击落的飞机是一架 Su-34 战斗轰炸机和一架 Su-35 战斗机，但没有透露被击落的地区。周末，乌克兰表示在东部天空击落了三架俄罗斯 Su-34 和一架 Su-35。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/russia-loses-six-warplanes-in-three-days-ukraine-says/articleshow/107824655.cms</guid></item><item><title>欧盟开始对 TikTok 儿童保护问题展开正式调查</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-begins-formal-probe-into-tiktok-over-child-protection/articleshow/107824255.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107824255.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧盟 (EU) 已对 TikTok 发起正式调查，原因是其可能违反旨在保护未成年人在线的规则。这项调查是根据一项强制监管数字内容的法律进行的。去年11月，欧盟还对YouTube和TikTok发起调查，以评估这些平台正在采取的措施。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 11:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/eu-begins-formal-probe-into-tiktok-over-child-protection/articleshow/107824255.cms</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军队与穆斯林武装分子发生枪战，造成至少八人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/philippine-troops-clash-with-muslim-militants-in-a-gunbattle-that-has-left-at-least-eight-dead/articleshow/107821063.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107821063.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 10:44:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/philippine-troops-clash-with-muslim-militants-in-a-gunbattle-that-has-left-at-least-eight-dead/articleshow/107821063.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人在联合国最高法院指责以色列实行“种族隔离”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-accuse-israel-of-apartheid-at-un-top-court/articleshow/107820231.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107820231.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴勒斯坦外交部长里亚德·马尔基周一向联合国最高法院表示，巴勒斯坦人民在以色列占领下遭受着“殖民主义和种族隔离”，法官正在权衡以色列占领的法律后果。 “巴勒斯坦人忍受了殖民主义和种族隔离......有些人对这些话感到愤怒。他们应该对我们所遭受的现实感到愤怒，”马尔基说。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/palestinians-accuse-israel-of-apartheid-at-un-top-court/articleshow/107820231.cms</guid></item><item><title>阿富汗雪崩六人死亡多人被困</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/people-killed-several-trapped-in-afghanistan-avalanche/articleshow/107815292.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107815292.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿富汗东部努里斯坦省遭遇雪崩，该地区遭遇大雪，造成 25 人死亡，另有几人可能被困。雪崩袭击了塔廷山谷的纳克雷村，房屋被雪和瓦砾掩埋，导致约 20 栋房屋严重受损。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:46:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/people-killed-several-trapped-in-afghanistan-avalanche/articleshow/107815292.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚部落冲突造成数十人死亡：ABC</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dozens-killed-in-tribal-fighting-in-papua-new-guinea-abc/articleshow/107819439.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107819439.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚广播公司 (ABC) 周一援引当地警方消息称，巴布亚新几内亚北部高地的部落战斗已造成至少 26 人死亡。据澳大利亚国家广播公司报道，这些人在恩加省的一次伏击中被杀。当地报纸《信使邮报》报道称，暴力事件发生在周日，与两个部落之间的战斗有关。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 09:29:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dozens-killed-in-tribal-fighting-in-papua-new-guinea-abc/articleshow/107819439.cms</guid></item><item><title>“总统伟大”：唐纳德·特朗普在新民意调查中排名垫底</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/presidential-greatness-donald-trump-ranks-last-in-new-poll/articleshow/107815083.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107815083.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最新的专家民意调查将亚伯拉罕·林肯列为最重要的美国总统，而唐纳德·特朗普则排名垫底。富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福、乔治·华盛顿、泰迪·罗斯福和托马斯·杰斐逊也排名很高。乔·拜登排名第 14 位。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 07:28:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/presidential-greatness-donald-trump-ranks-last-in-new-poll/articleshow/107815083.cms</guid></item><item><title>德国在核武器方面的艰难历史</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germanys-difficult-history-with-nuclear-weapons/articleshow/107812377.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107812377.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托利斯驳回了有关欧洲核武器的争论，强调美欧关系。历史背景：德国在二战后放弃了核武器。冷战期间，美国曾在西德部署核弹头。专家认为，由于后勤方面的挑战和国际承诺，德国拥有核武器是不现实的。尽管受到特朗普的影响，北约关系仍保持弹性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/germanys-difficult-history-with-nuclear-weapons/articleshow/107812377.cms</guid></item><item><title>如果没有塔利班，联合国阿富汗会议能否成功？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/can-un-afghanistan-conference-succeed-without-the-taliban/articleshow/107812551.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107812551.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 06:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/can-un-afghanistan-conference-succeed-without-the-taliban/articleshow/107812551.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴西总统卢拉将加沙战争比作“大屠杀”；以色列回应</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/brazil-president-lulas-compares-gaza-war-to-holocaust-israel-responds/articleshow/107809099.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107809099.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列谴责巴西总统卢拉·达席尔瓦将以色列在加沙地带的行动比作大屠杀并称之为种族灭绝的言论。以色列总理表示，他“轻视大屠杀并试图伤害犹太人民和以色列自卫权，从而跨越了红线”。以色列总理和外交部长还召见巴西大使进行“严厉谴责”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 05:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/brazil-president-lulas-compares-gaza-war-to-holocaust-israel-responds/articleshow/107809099.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>